# Personal task files — local to each machine, not shared.
# The two task files below are runtime dependencies (read by the launchd
# jobs and proactive/sweep.ts), so they stay tracked, as do the plist
# templates install.sh deploys from.
tasks/*.md
!tasks/EXAMPLE-task.md
!tasks/inbox-brief.md
!tasks/proactive-calendar.md
